## Additional known issue, newly exposed by A1

`test/test_dry_flux_interface.jl` segfaults under Julia 1.12 codegen
in the "Mass conservation (zonal flow)" testset at line 425. The
segfault PRE-EXISTS A2's cleanup (verified by running the file on
pristine `surface-emissions` tip before the A2 edits). The hypothesis
in PRE_PLAN_18_FIXES §A2 ("duplicate include likely cause") is not
supported by the evidence. The segfault is a Julia 1.12 codegen bug
in an unrelated testset; plan 18 does not try to fix it, but it
remains a known-bad state for this file.

